end
opt supported mutable drift is detected
ServiceManager -> OCI: Apply ChangeRoverClusterCompartment,\nUpdateRoverCluster only for mutable\nfields clusterSize,\nclusterWorkloads,\ncustomerShippingAddress,\ndataValidationCode (+16 more)
loop update pending UPDATING
ServiceManager -> OCI: GetRoverCluster
end
end
